.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, grapefruit, peach, potato
House: wooden, victorian, craftsman, cottage
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, turtle
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, magic-tricks, filmmaking, traveling
 1. the craftsman house is the person eating peach##1
 2. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the cottage house##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 7. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 8. the owner of the cat is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the victorian house##2
 9. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
10. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Food          | grapefruit | potato  | cauliflower | peach      |
| House   | wooden       | cottage    | victorian      | craftsman      |
| Pet           | turtle     | cat     | dog         | hedgehog   |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | card-games | magic-tricks     | traveling |

