4. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
5. the french is the person traveling to hamburg##1
6. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
8. the person playing monopoly is between the owner of the chinchilla and the polish##2
9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
| Game           | bridge     | monopoly | mah-jongg | go |
| City   | nizza     | prague       | liverpool      | hamburg   |
| Nationality   | canadian   | australian   | polish    | french       |
| Pet           | chinchilla | horse        | rabbit    | snake        |

