4 different pets are kept: turtle, frog, goldfish, dog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, cycling, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 2. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 9. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the owner of the dog is between the person drinking almond-milk and the owner of the goldfish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | almond-milk | fanta     | cola       |
| Transport          | bike   | train    | subway | ship       |
| Pet   | turtle     | frog       | dog    | goldfish     |
