 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 6. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the blend-smoker is the fan of r&b##1
10. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
11. the person who growslily is the person who's hobby is chess##1

