.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, radish, watermelon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, blues, techno, pop
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, mystery, satire
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, milk, sprite
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 4. the fan of blues is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking 7up##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is between the fan of blues and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the fan of pop##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person eating radish is the fan of blues##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | blueberry | watermelon   | radish   | artichoke |
| Music-Genre           | funk   | techno     | blues   | pop |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure    | satire   | mystery   |
| Beverage         | iced-tea    | 7up | sprite | milk    |

 